-- New York City Schools Chancellor Joel Klein Plans to Step Down, WNBC Says
-- B y   B i l l   K o e n i g
-- 2010-11-09T20:07:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-09/new-york-city-schools-chancellor-joel-klein-plans-to-step-down-wnbc-says.html
New York City Schools Chancellor Joel
Klein is getting ready to depart office, NBCNewYork.com
reported, citing people familiar with the situation it didn’t
identify.  Klein’s resignation may be disclosed as early as this
afternoon, NBCNewYork.com said.    To contact the editor responsible for this story:
